FEMALE NUTRITIONIST / DIETICIAN
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 14:08:54
Ref. JB3047168
Job Description
Reporting to the Director, the Fitness Nutritionist will be responsible for educating and helping ladies on effective ways to improve their health, optimize their performance and manage their weight based on their overall health objectives.
Responsibilities:
•	Nutritionist may advise individuals on dietary practices, exercise and use of vitamins, minerals and supplements.
•	Setting nutritious monthly diet plans based on clients’ likes, dislikes, allergies and overall fitness achievements.
•	Amend set to go meal plans according to clients goals
•	Assist Fitness Personal Trainers in educating female clients to achieve their goals by combining a nutrition with fitness
•	Meet new clients and follow up with existing ones.
•	Provide assistance to Miss Fitness whenever is required
Skills
•	A degree in Human Nutrition
•	At least two years’ experience working in nutrition or as a Dietician
•	Excellent communication skills in English
•	Must have a valid UAE driving license
•	Strong computer literacy
Dietician; Fitness, Nutritionist, Health, Dubai, UAE,
